  "detailed_description": "<strong><i>Sentimental K</i> is a 3D roguelike action game.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/ecee9ceb895097e26c5a819cfc27bcc7.poster.avif?t=1732950583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/ecee9ceb895097e26c5a819cfc27bcc7.webm?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/ecee9ceb895097e26c5a819cfc27bcc7.mp4?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Sentimental K</i> blends the dynamic, intuitive gameplay of 3D action games with the unpredictable and ever-changing nature of roguelikes.<br><br>Players must defeat enemies and progress towards their goal using 『Weapons, Skills, and Artifacts』 obtained from various situations. If players die during their journey, they lose all their rewards and must restart from the beginning.<br><br>With 5 weapons, 78 skills, 132 artifacts, 13 bosses, and randomly generated dungeon layouts, each playthrough is unique. You'll need to find your own optimal configurations to make it all the way to the end!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Dynamic Action and 3D Action Camera</strong><br>With our extensive experience in action game development, we've crafted Sentimental K with tight controls and dynamic 3D action that remains visceral and rhythmic. The game primarily uses a top-down view, but the camera dynamically adjusts for an optimal player experience.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/8d22c8a971ed0c466c9ecadaac772ec9.poster.avif?t=1732950583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/8d22c8a971ed0c466c9ecadaac772ec9.webm?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/8d22c8a971ed0c466c9ecadaac772ec9.mp4?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unique Boss Concepts</strong><br>Sentimental K's bosses are designed around specific emotions. Explore and conquer these unique challenges!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/1c05534824648352bd1c8ea950a9ff4c.poster.avif?t=1732950583\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/1c05534824648352bd1c8ea950a9ff4c.webm?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/1c05534824648352bd1c8ea950a9ff4c.mp4?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Deep, Synergistic Strategies</strong><br>Players must carefully consider how to effectively combine the 『Weapons, Skills, and Artifacts』 they acquire. Create your own synergy builds to conquer the dungeons!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/5e0405bc149492937bd28812d5847aa1.poster.avif?t=1732950583\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/5e0405bc149492937bd28812d5847aa1.webm?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/5e0405bc149492937bd28812d5847aa1.mp4?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Randomness</strong><br>Weapons, skills, artifacts, bosses, dungeon layouts, and other elements are randomly generated, ensuring a fresh experience every time you play.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/7797efe5496a30edacb018f695203ae3.poster.avif?t=1732950583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/7797efe5496a30edacb018f695203ae3.webm?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/7797efe5496a30edacb018f695203ae3.mp4?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Permadeath</strong><br>Unfortunately, if you're killed by a monster, you must start over from the beginning with only your basic weapon. Your character's stats do not permanently improve; instead, your growth as a player and your immersive experience drive progress.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/1501e21f67fad7f59734e95a6c6cde8e.poster.avif?t=1732950583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/1501e21f67fad7f59734e95a6c6cde8e.webm?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256530/extras/1501e21f67fad7f59734e95a6c6cde8e.mp4?t=1732950583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
